                    <tr>
                      <td width="230" valign="top"><h1>Welcome!</h1>
                        <p>                          Come out to the Halton County Radial Railway for an experience you won&rsquo;t forget. Your admission gives you access to display barns, railway station AND unlimited rides! Free parking is also available.</p>
                        <p>See our <a href="ab_admission.html">hours of operation and admission rates</a>.</p>
                      <a href="http://twitter.com/streetcarmuseum"><img src="images/twitter.gif" alt="Follow us on Twitter" width="160" height="27" border="0" /></a></td>
                      <td width="20" valign="top">&nbsp;</td>
                      <td width="400" valign="top"><p><iframe width="400" height="252" src="http://www.youtube.com/embed/XEpGUhYrD_c?rel=0" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe></p>
                      <p>Video production by <a href="http://www.openconceptfilms.com" target="new">Open Concept Films</a>.</p></td>
